       <a href="../../../../../org/apache/http/client/HttpClient.html" title="interface in org.apache.http.client"><code>HttpClient</code></a> pre-configured for most common use scenarios.

       <p> Additional interceptors can be added as follows, but take care not to add the same interceptor more than once. </p>
       <pre>
 DefaultHttpClient httpclient = new DefaultHttpClient();
 httpclient.addRequestInterceptor(new RequestAcceptEncoding());
 httpclient.addResponseInterceptor(new ResponseContentEncoding());
 </pre> 
       <p> This class sets up the following parameters if not explicitly set: </p>
